      <title>最高法院判决韩国同性伴侣在配偶身份问题上胜诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/top-court-hands-south-korean-gay-couple-win-on-spouse-status</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最高法院裁定一对同性伴侣申请配偶医疗保险可享受国民健康保险福利，这一具有里程碑意义的裁决可能为韩国承认同性婚姻铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/top-court-hands-south-korean-gay-couple-win-on-spouse-status</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:48:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>抗议活动升级，孟加拉国面临全国停工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/bangladesh-faces-nationwide-shutdown-as-jobs-protest-escalates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周早些时候的示威活动演变为暴力事件，孟加拉国学生抗议领袖要求从周四开始全天关闭交通网络和企业，并向总理谢赫·哈西娜施加压力，要求其废除政府的就业配额制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/bangladesh-faces-nationwide-shutdown-as-jobs-protest-escalates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:14:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
